title: Yay for Ye? Warning: FBI Agents Partying 6.4.18
itunes:title: Yay for Ye? Warning: FBI Agents Partying 6.4.18
description:
In episode 161, Jack and Miles are joined by frequent podcast guest and comedian Jamie Loftus to discuss their thoughts on the new Kanye West, the Supreme Court's decision on Masterpiece Cakes vs. gay couple, Trump's shamelessness when it comes to North Korea and more, Trump's plan for pardoning himself, Bill Clinton's new book tour, an FBI agent firing his gun after doing a backflip, and more!
